---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body class="font-sans antialiased">
    <Header />
    <div class="h-20"></div>
    <main class="px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>
      <section class="mb-8">
        <p class="mb-4">
          Hello! I'm Shubhanshu Pandey, a passionate web developer with a love for modern web technologies. I have extensive experience working with various web development tools and frameworks, including Vite, Tailwind CSS, and Astro. My journey in web development began [X] years ago, and since then, I have been constantly learning and evolving with the industry.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The purpose of this blog is to share my knowledge and experience with fellow developers and tech enthusiasts. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned developer, my goal is to provide valuable insights, tutorials, and best practices that can help you on your journey.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          When I'm not coding, I enjoy [hobbies/interests], and I love exploring new technologies and staying up-to-date with the latest trends in the tech world.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <section class="mb-8">
        <p class="mb-4">
          On this blog, you can expect to find:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
          <li>In-depth tutorials on Vite, Tailwind CSS, and Astro</li>
          <li>Tips and best practices for modern web development</li>
          <li>Articles on the latest trends and technologies in web development</li>
          <li>Personal insights and experiences from my journey as a developer</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Stay Connected</h2>
      <section>
        <p class="mb-4">
          I love connecting with fellow developers and tech enthusiasts. Feel free to reach out to me on [social media platforms] or through the contact form on this blog. Let's learn and grow together!
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
